    "description": "Goblin Colony 是一款具有建筑和定居点管理功能的实时战略游戏。作为地下城的守护者，你将指挥一个雄心勃勃的地精部落，挖掘、建造和探索山脉深处。在与矮人和其他生物争夺霸权的过程中，掌控全局！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造你的殖民地</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/38a79489471fd514399e63c13a3e4826.poster.avif?t=1757201735\" width=608 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/38a79489471fd514399e63c13a3e4826.webm?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/38a79489471fd514399e63c13a3e4826.mp4?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>扩大你的地下城并按你想要的方式塑造它。<br><br>建造一个堡垒，里面有金库、兵营等房间。<br><br>放置火把照亮前进的道路。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挖掘探索</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/7ff561b733b9ea77b971a8c01147074f.poster.avif?t=1757201735\" width=608 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/7ff561b733b9ea77b971a8c01147074f.webm?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/7ff561b733b9ea77b971a8c01147074f.mp4?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>挖掘地牢寻找黄金。<br><br>通过建造桥梁跨越河流。<br>小心危险的敌人，例如变异老鼠和巨型飞蝙蝠。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理地精</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/4a232dacdaca925d0220cd04aca384ed.poster.avif?t=1757201735\" width=608 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/4a232dacdaca925d0220cd04aca384ed.webm?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/4a232dacdaca925d0220cd04aca384ed.mp4?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>根据地精的需求为其提供床铺，饥饿时提供食物。<br>研究新技术以助您进步。<br>招募地精作为战士与敌人作战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与敌人作战</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/f795e1b5bae8788cfadd7c7fb8c76c02.poster.avif?t=1757201735\" width=608 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/f795e1b5bae8788cfadd7c7fb8c76c02.webm?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2276800/extras/f795e1b5bae8788cfadd7c7fb8c76c02.mp4?t=1757201735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>与矮人和怪物战斗，争夺霸权。<br>制造攻城武器来保卫您的基地。<br>通过人数优势或巧妙的战术取得胜利。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 适合休闲玩家和硬核玩家的实时战略游戏<br></li><li> 包含 15 张以上地图的大型战役<br></li><li> 带有随机地图的遭遇战模式<br></li><li> 用户制作的地图<br></li><li> 包含关卡编辑器！</li></ul>",
